source.name: Stalled Construction Sites
source.description: an overview of sites across the five boroughs where construction activity has come to an abrupt halt.  Now updated daily on NYC Open Data from April 10, 2013 onward.  Prior weekly reports are archived at DOB and are not available on NYC Open Data.
